The '''''Chandrila Moon''''' was a [[Marketta-class shuttle|''Marketta''-class shuttle]] carried aboard the [[Protector (Victory-class)|''Protector'']] in [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]]. [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] rode it from the ''Protector'' to the [[Bastion customs station]] to meet [[Gilad Pellaeon/Legends|Gilad Pellaeon]].

